'''毛衣女郎'''是1940-1950年代[[美國|美國]]的流行用語，原指當時享譽盛名的幾位[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]女星，諸如[[拉娜·特納|拉娜·特納]]、[[珍·曼絲菲|珍·曼絲菲]]與[[珍·羅素|珍·羅素]]。她們穿著[[羊絨|羊絨]]或{{le|安哥拉絨|Angora wool}}材質的修身[[毛衣|毛衣]]與[[胸罩款式列表|子彈胸罩]]，以強調女性的胸部曲線。
<ref>{{cite book | last = Herbst | first = Philip  | title = Wimmin, wimps & wallflowers: an encyclopaedic dictionary of gender and sexual orientation bias in the United States | publisher = Intercultural Press | year = 2001 | page = [https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781877864803/page/122 122] | url = https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781877864803| url-access = registration | isbn = 978-1-877864-80-3 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Ostler | first = Rosemarie | title = Dewdroppers, waldos, and slackers: a decade-by-decade guide to the vanishing vocabulary of the twentieth century | publisher = Oxford University Press US | year = 2005 | pages = 85 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=qD6SwN7oZ9wC&pg=PA85&dq=%22Sweater+girl%22&lr=&as_brr=3&client=firefox-a#v=onepage&q=%22Sweater%20girl%22&f=false | isbn = 978-0-19-518254-5 | access-date = 2020-09-26 | archive-date = 2017-02-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170216202950/https://books.google.com/books?id=qD6SwN7oZ9wC&pg=PA85&dq=%22Sweater+girl%22&lr=&as_brr=3&client=firefox-a#v=onepage&q=%22Sweater%20girl%22&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>

這股時尚為當時的青少年鍾愛，「毛衣女郎」也轉變為一種流行類型的指稱，甚至與戰後反權威的青少年[[次文化|次文化]]、「道德敗壞」、「傷風敗俗」產生連結。如{{le|匹茲堡警司|Pittsburgh Police}}Harvey J. Scott所言:「婦女穿著凸顯曲線的衣服招搖過市，這就是毛衣女郎──純粹幼稚的招蜂引蝶。她們將成為什麼樣的母親和妻子？」
